{
  "info": {
    "name": "MG Plastic — Social Links (Plumber + Store)",
    "_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-social-4000-9000-mgsociallinks",
    "description": "# روابط التواصل الاجتماعي\n\n## Setup\n1. ضع `base_url` = `https://mg-plastic.com` أو `http://mgplastic.test`\n2. سجّل دخول سبّاك → يتخزن `plumber_token`\n3. سجّل دخول متجر (موزّع/تاجر) → يتخزن `store_token`\n\n## Platforms المقبولة\n`facebook` · `instagram` · `whatsapp` · `twitter` · `youtube` · `tiktok` · `website` · `snapchat`\n\nAliases: `fb` `ig` `wa` `x` `yt` `tt` `snap` + أسماء عربية\n\n## صيغ الـ Body المقبولة (POST upsert)\n1. **مصفوفة links** (الموصى بها)\n2. **خريطة platform → url**\n3. **رابط واحد** `{ platform, url }`\n4. **JSON string** داخل `links` (multipart)\n5. **متداخل** `{ data: { links: [...] } }`\n6. **aliases للحقول**: `link` / `href` / `value` بدل `url` · `type` بدل `platform`\n7. واتساب: رقم فقط `0912345678` → يتحول `https://wa.me/...`\n8. يوزرنيم: `@plumber` → رابط المنصة\n\nالروابط الفارغة تُتجاهل (التطبيق يقدر يبعت كل المنصات).\n\n## حذف — Best practice\n| الطريقة | متى |\n|---|---|\n| **DELETE .../social-links/facebook** | الأفضل للموبايل — ثابت، idempotent، بدون تخزين id |\n| **DELETE .../social-links/{{link_id}}** | بعد List/Upsert لو معاك الـ id الرقمي |\n\nكلا الطريقتين مدعومان.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "https://mg-plastic.com", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "plumber_phone", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "plumber_password", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "plumber_token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "store_phone", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "store_password", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "store_token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "link_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "store_link_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "plumber_store_id", "value": "3", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "0 — Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login Plumber",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "const token = json?.data?.token || json?.token;",
                  "if (token) pm.collectionVariables.set('plumber_token', token);",
                  "pm.test('plumber login', () => pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.be.oneOf([200, 201]));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"{{plumber_phone}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{plumber_password}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "login"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login Store (Distributor / Trader)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
